Title: Quantum $\kappa$-Poincare in Any Dimensions

Authors: Jerzy Lukierski and Henri Ruegg

Comments: (PLAIN TeX, 10 pp. )

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B329 (1994) 189-194

The $\kappa$-deformation of the D-dimensional Poincar\'e algebra $(D\geq 2)$with any signature is given. Further the quadratic Poisson brackets, determinedby the classical $r$-matrix are calculated, and the quantum Poincar\'e group"with noncommuting parameters" is obtained.